description: Twohey’s restaurant has been serving up memories since 1943, and now its food truck is keeping the tradition alive and makin’ those memories mobile. If you’re a fan of all-American fare, then you've met your match with this renowned retro truck. Twohey’s offers a medley of menus, including classic burgers, barbecue, and of course their award-winning soda fountain and famous hot fudge sundaes. You can even customize and create your own menu, woohoo!With this incredible selection and their top-of-the-line features (including flat-screen TVs and an impressive sound system) you too will be a fan of Twohey’s truck.
name: Twohey's
